```

Iterate from 0 to n-1 using range over an integer (Go 1.22+).

```go
for i := range 10 {
    fmt.Println(i) // 0..9
}
```

Range over a function that yields values via a callback (Go 1.22+).

```go
for v := range myIterator {
    fmt.Println(v)
}

// Iterator signature:
