A test function for `go test`. Must start with `Test` and accept `*testing.T`.

```go
func TestSomething(t *testing.T) {
    got := Add(1, 2)
    if got != 3 {
        t.Errorf("Add(1,2) = %d, want 3", got)
    }
}
```

A benchmark function for `go test -bench`. Must start with `Benchmark` and accept `*testing.B`.

```go
func BenchmarkSomething(b *testing.B) {
    for i := 0; i < b.N; i++ {
        // code to benchmark
    }
}
```

